WEBVTT

00:00:07.716 --> 00:00:08.885
- [panting]

00:00:08.918 --> 00:00:11.155
<i>- You're not getting away!</i>

00:00:13.059 --> 00:00:14.028
[footstep scrapes]

00:00:14.061 --> 00:00:15.798
- [gasps]

00:00:15.832 --> 00:00:17.034
[whimpers]

00:00:17.067 --> 00:00:20.273
- [yells]

00:00:21.075 --> 00:00:24.048
<i>It's tiny and hard to target.</i>

00:00:24.081 --> 00:00:26.453
- [whimpers]

00:00:26.486 --> 00:00:28.356
[gags]

00:00:29.158 --> 00:00:30.729
<i>- All right! I can do it!</i>

00:00:30.762 --> 00:00:33.767
- [wailing]

00:00:37.842 --> 00:00:39.847
<i>["Kizuna no Kiseki" playing]</i>

00:00:39.880 --> 00:00:47.094
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:02:09.860 --> 00:02:11.863
<i>[singers vocalizing]</i>

00:02:15.838 --> 00:02:17.842
- [wailing]
- [sword grinding]

00:02:19.780 --> 00:02:20.882
- [grunting]

00:02:20.915 --> 00:02:22.619
<i>What a horrible voice!</i>

00:02:22.653 --> 00:02:23.654
<i>My ears!</i>

00:02:24.656 --> 00:02:26.827
<i>Even so, I can do it!</i>

00:02:26.860 --> 00:02:27.829
<i>I can behead it!</i>

00:02:27.862 --> 00:02:30.434
- [shrieking]

00:02:30.467 --> 00:02:31.637
- [gasps]

00:02:31.670 --> 00:02:33.406
<i>[ominous music]</i>

00:02:34.609 --> 00:02:35.679
<i>What is that?</i>

00:02:35.712 --> 00:02:37.181
<i>Something's behind me.</i>

00:02:37.214 --> 00:02:39.485
<i>There's something behind me!</i>

00:02:41.188 --> 00:02:42.792
<i>Joy! Anger!</i>

00:02:42.826 --> 00:02:44.630
<i>Sorrow! Pleasure!</i>

00:02:44.663 --> 00:02:47.301
<i>This doesn't smell
like any of them!</i>

00:02:47.334 --> 00:02:49.071
<i>Then what's behind me?</i>

00:02:49.104 --> 00:02:50.407
<i>What do I do?!</i>

00:02:52.712 --> 00:02:54.015
- [wailing]

00:02:54.048 --> 00:02:56.285
<i>- Focus on beheading this one!</i>

00:02:56.318 --> 00:02:58.223
<i>If I behead this one, then...</i>

00:02:58.256 --> 00:03:02.264
- [wailing]

00:03:02.297 --> 00:03:03.433
<i>- It's too hard!</i>

00:03:03.466 --> 00:03:05.504
<i>I can't slash any further.</i>

00:03:05.538 --> 00:03:08.109
<i>And the power from
Nezuko's blood has run out!</i>

00:03:08.143 --> 00:03:10.047
- Tanjiro! Get down!

00:03:10.080 --> 00:03:11.383
<i>- I can't do it.</i>

00:03:11.416 --> 00:03:13.319
<i>I made the wrong call!</i>

00:03:13.352 --> 00:03:15.323
<i>And because of my position,</i>

00:03:15.356 --> 00:03:17.796
<i>Genya can't fire his gun
without hitting me!</i>

00:03:17.829 --> 00:03:18.798
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

00:03:18.831 --> 00:03:22.471
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:03:22.505 --> 00:03:23.507
<i>Crap!</i>

00:03:24.308 --> 00:03:25.277
[drum pounds]

00:03:25.310 --> 00:03:26.680
<i>Here comes the attack!</i>

00:03:30.054 --> 00:03:32.859
[rumbling]

00:03:35.965 --> 00:03:37.435
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

00:03:37.468 --> 00:03:39.640
<i>[singers vocalizing]</i>

00:03:39.673 --> 00:03:46.686
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:04:00.180 --> 00:04:01.650
[gasps]

00:04:03.888 --> 00:04:06.794
[Nezuko winces]

00:04:06.827 --> 00:04:07.962
- Nezuko!

00:04:07.996 --> 00:04:09.566
[flesh stretches]

00:04:10.668 --> 00:04:11.670
[groans]

00:04:12.672 --> 00:04:13.841
[gasps]

00:04:15.411 --> 00:04:17.348
Nezuko! Are you all right?

00:04:17.381 --> 00:04:19.586
- [grunting]

00:04:21.590 --> 00:04:22.893
- Nezuko!

00:04:22.926 --> 00:04:24.328
- [sighing]

00:04:25.932 --> 00:04:27.334
<i>- She'll be fine.</i>

00:04:27.367 --> 00:04:29.839
<i>Her arms and legs
have fully regenerated!</i>

00:04:31.042 --> 00:04:32.746
- [sighing]

00:04:32.779 --> 00:04:34.281
- [gasps]

00:04:35.518 --> 00:04:38.824
- You brutal fiends
who torment the weak...

00:04:40.293 --> 00:04:43.499
you're atrocious, offensive...

00:04:44.736 --> 00:04:46.071
and despicable!

00:04:49.879 --> 00:04:51.282
- [gasps]

00:04:51.315 --> 00:04:57.796
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:04:57.829 --> 00:05:00.534
- Damn you all,
you awful villains.

00:05:02.304 --> 00:05:03.807
<i>- Another demon?</i>

00:05:03.840 --> 00:05:04.909
<i>There's six?!</i>

00:05:05.912 --> 00:05:07.715
<i>Five's already too many.</i>

00:05:07.749 --> 00:05:09.819
And we have to fight
another one?!

00:05:11.155 --> 00:05:13.794
<i>Wait, that's not a sixth demon.</i>

00:05:15.865 --> 00:05:17.067
<i>The four Emotions...</i>

00:05:18.169 --> 00:05:20.407
<i>there's no trace of them
anymore!</i>

00:05:20.440 --> 00:05:22.712
[wind blowing]

00:05:22.745 --> 00:05:24.749
<i>- What the hell's going on?!</i>

00:05:24.783 --> 00:05:27.121
<i>How many tricks
do they have up their sleeve?!</i>

00:05:27.154 --> 00:05:28.858
<i>I'm positive that one</i>

00:05:28.891 --> 00:05:31.630
<i>was the Anger Demon
just a second ago!</i>

00:05:33.099 --> 00:05:35.871
<i>Something happened
the moment Tanjiro's sword</i>

00:05:35.905 --> 00:05:38.577
<i>was about to decapitate
that tiny demon.</i>

00:05:39.512 --> 00:05:41.316
<i>[ominous music]</i>

00:05:41.349 --> 00:05:44.856
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:05:44.889 --> 00:05:47.828
<i>The Anger Demon
raised both of his hands...</i>

00:05:49.566 --> 00:05:52.506
<i>and in the blink of an eye,
he was able to absorb...</i>

00:05:52.539 --> 00:05:55.009
<i>the Joy Demon
and the Pleasure Demon!</i>

00:05:56.145 --> 00:05:57.883
<i>He pulverized their flesh</i>

00:05:57.916 --> 00:06:01.256
<i>and then continued
absorbing both of them.</i>

00:06:01.289 --> 00:06:02.257
<i>[singers vocalizing]</i>

00:06:02.290 --> 00:06:03.927
<i>Then after drawing them in,</i>

00:06:03.960 --> 00:06:07.835
<i>the Anger Demon started
sprinting towards Aizetsu.</i>

00:06:07.869 --> 00:06:11.610
<i>I saw Aizetsu start to open
his mouth, as if to protest,</i>

00:06:11.644 --> 00:06:15.149
<i>but he was absorbed
before he could speak!</i>

00:06:16.385 --> 00:06:20.928
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:06:20.961 --> 00:06:23.868
<i>The Anger Demon's body
transformed</i>

00:06:23.901 --> 00:06:25.638
<i>and turned into that!</i>

00:06:28.076 --> 00:06:29.912
- [gurgles]

00:06:31.148 --> 00:06:33.053
<i>- You've gotta be kidding me.</i>

00:06:33.086 --> 00:06:34.790
<i>[singers vocalizing]</i>

00:06:34.823 --> 00:06:37.596
<i>He absorbed
the three other demons?</i>

00:06:37.629 --> 00:06:39.498
<i>He fused with them?!</i>

00:06:42.070 --> 00:06:43.072
- [gasps]

00:06:51.890 --> 00:06:55.330
<i>- This wasn't a split,
but he still got even younger!</i>

00:06:55.363 --> 00:06:57.502
<i>He's a kid...</i>

00:06:57.535 --> 00:06:59.739
<i>a fusion of the demons
without the old geezer,</i>

00:06:59.772 --> 00:07:01.510
<i>who's most likely the main body!</i>

00:07:01.543 --> 00:07:04.549
- [whimpers]

00:07:04.582 --> 00:07:06.051
[drum pounds]

00:07:08.456 --> 00:07:10.962
<i>- Oh, no! The main body's
being surrounded!</i>

00:07:10.995 --> 00:07:11.963
Hold it!

00:07:11.997 --> 00:07:13.199
- [grunts]

00:07:13.232 --> 00:07:14.201
- [sputters]

00:07:14.234 --> 00:07:17.174
<i>[tense music]</i>

00:07:17.207 --> 00:07:25.023
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:07:25.056 --> 00:07:26.426
<i>[singers vocalizing]</i>

00:07:26.459 --> 00:07:28.496
<i>It's so overpowering.</i>

00:07:28.530 --> 00:07:29.967
<i>I can't breathe!</i>

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:35.043
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:07:35.076 --> 00:07:36.813
<i>My heart hurts.</i>

00:07:37.915 --> 00:07:40.521
- [shuddering]

00:07:45.030 --> 00:07:46.766
- What's wrong?

00:07:47.569 --> 00:07:48.938
Answer me.

00:07:48.971 --> 00:07:50.774
Do you have a problem
with what I'm doing,

00:07:50.808 --> 00:07:53.212
or can I continue my duty here?

00:07:54.215 --> 00:07:55.785
- [groans]

00:07:55.818 --> 00:07:57.387
- [shudders]

00:07:57.420 --> 00:07:58.957
- [sighs]

00:08:01.428 --> 00:08:03.099
- Well?

00:08:03.132 --> 00:08:06.105
Do you, awful villains?

00:08:10.246 --> 00:08:11.416
- [shudders]

00:08:11.449 --> 00:08:12.952
<i>So heavy.</i>

00:08:12.985 --> 00:08:14.288
<i>That voice...</i>

00:08:14.321 --> 00:08:15.557
<i>that force...</i>

00:08:16.726 --> 00:08:20.166
<i>it's sapping all the strength
I have in my limbs.</i>

00:08:20.199 --> 00:08:22.605
<i>I can barely stay on my feet!</i>

00:08:30.888 --> 00:08:31.923
- [gasps]

00:08:31.957 --> 00:08:32.958
Tell me...

00:08:35.263 --> 00:08:36.834
what makes--

00:08:36.867 --> 00:08:40.574
what makes us awful villains
and not you?

00:08:41.843 --> 00:08:45.852
- Because you made the choice
to torment the weak, right?

00:08:45.885 --> 00:08:47.688
Or did you
not just try to decapitate

00:08:47.722 --> 00:08:49.024
a small, weak being

00:08:49.058 --> 00:08:52.230
who's only big enough
to fit in the palm of your hand?

00:08:53.633 --> 00:08:55.804
- [whimpering]

00:09:03.085 --> 00:09:06.058
<i>- Your actions
are utterly atrocious.</i>

00:09:06.091 --> 00:09:09.599
<i>Only a pure fiend
would do something like that!</i>

00:09:11.369 --> 00:09:14.542
- Did you just say
small and weak?

00:09:14.575 --> 00:09:16.412
<i>[tense music]</i>

00:09:16.445 --> 00:09:20.019
Small--Small and weak?

00:09:20.053 --> 00:09:21.723
Don't give me that!

00:09:22.659 --> 00:09:24.696
That scent you're
giving off right now,

00:09:24.730 --> 00:09:26.299
the scent of blood,

00:09:26.332 --> 00:09:29.806
a scent like that means you've
devoured hundreds of humans!

00:09:30.942 --> 00:09:33.814
What did those people do
to deserve that fate?!

00:09:33.847 --> 00:09:34.650
- [sighs]

00:09:34.683 --> 00:09:36.218
- Tell me what they did!

00:09:36.251 --> 00:09:37.154
What could they have done

00:09:37.187 --> 00:09:39.291
that would have
cost them their lives?!

00:09:40.828 --> 00:09:42.665
Don't you dare
play the victim card

00:09:42.698 --> 00:09:45.571
after devouring
scores of innocent people!

00:09:45.604 --> 00:09:48.310
If there's one thing
I'm certain of,

00:09:48.343 --> 00:09:50.046
it's that you're evil!

00:09:51.784 --> 00:09:53.554
You're the villain.

00:09:53.587 --> 00:09:56.325
And I'll be the one
that decapitates you!

00:09:56.358 --> 00:10:02.705
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:10:02.738 --> 00:10:04.609
<i>[wind blowing]</i>

00:10:04.642 --> 00:10:05.944
<i>[sword slices]</i>

00:10:09.752 --> 00:10:11.623
<i>[wind blowing]</i>

00:10:11.656 --> 00:10:13.159
<i>[sword slices]</i>

00:10:14.762 --> 00:10:16.700
<i>[tense music]</i>

00:10:16.733 --> 00:10:23.713
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:10:32.731 --> 00:10:36.038
[Genya shudders]

00:10:36.071 --> 00:10:37.742
<i>That demon...</i>

00:10:37.775 --> 00:10:39.679
<i>it's so overpowering.</i>

00:10:39.712 --> 00:10:41.950
<i>I still can't move a muscle!</i>

00:10:41.983 --> 00:10:43.185
- [gasps]

00:10:45.056 --> 00:10:47.695
<i>- Is that really
all you have to say?</i>

00:10:50.466 --> 00:10:53.773
- I will behead you,
no matter what!

00:10:55.076 --> 00:10:57.582
- Did I kill
a family member of yours?

00:10:57.615 --> 00:11:00.253
Is that why you're
so set on beheading me?

00:11:00.286 --> 00:11:02.390
- [gasps]

00:11:02.424 --> 00:11:03.425
No, but...

00:11:04.763 --> 00:11:08.002
- All right. Then this
has nothing to do with you.

00:11:08.035 --> 00:11:10.541
- You haven't killed anyone
dear to me,

00:11:10.574 --> 00:11:11.943
but that doesn't matter.

00:11:11.976 --> 00:11:14.549
Because you've slaughtered
innocent people

00:11:14.582 --> 00:11:16.753
who were dear to someone else!

00:11:16.787 --> 00:11:19.224
- It sounds like you
have nothing to do

00:11:19.258 --> 00:11:20.928
with those people, either.

00:11:20.962 --> 00:11:24.267
- Humans don't need a reason
to help out one another!

00:11:25.605 --> 00:11:28.610
And if you can't wrap your head
around something like that,

00:11:28.644 --> 00:11:29.646
you're the fiend!

00:11:29.679 --> 00:11:31.048
- [sputters]

00:11:31.081 --> 00:11:32.083
[drum pounds]

00:11:33.352 --> 00:11:35.323
[roar]

00:11:35.356 --> 00:11:36.693
[metal clangs]

00:11:36.727 --> 00:11:38.930
[water flowing]

00:11:52.758 --> 00:11:54.696
- Hyo, hyo, hyo!

00:11:54.729 --> 00:11:57.802
Oh, that fake
stoic look on your face,

00:11:57.835 --> 00:12:00.306
how very sublime it is!

00:12:00.339 --> 00:12:04.749
My creative juices are
simply gushing looking upon it!

00:12:08.557 --> 00:12:09.792
Don't get me wrong.

00:12:09.826 --> 00:12:11.796
I'd love to stick around
a little longer

00:12:11.829 --> 00:12:14.467
and watch as you meet
your pathetic end...

00:12:16.439 --> 00:12:18.910
but I think it's best
I look inside this shack

00:12:18.944 --> 00:12:20.881
that you were
so keen on entering.

00:12:22.083 --> 00:12:25.658
I'm trembling with excitement
to find out what's inside

00:12:25.691 --> 00:12:28.863
that you failed to protect.
Hyo, hyo, hyo!

00:12:31.503 --> 00:12:34.074
[water flowing]

00:12:35.443 --> 00:12:38.283
<i>- With the air left
inside of my lungs...</i>

00:12:38.316 --> 00:12:42.825
<i>I should be able to manage
one more attack!</i>

00:12:44.060 --> 00:12:47.000
<i>Mist Breathing, First Form...</i>

00:12:48.036 --> 00:12:50.206
<i>Low Clouds Distant Haze!</i>

00:12:55.350 --> 00:12:58.389
<i>Not even that was able
to break through it.</i>

00:12:58.422 --> 00:13:02.063
<i>It's no wonder, given
how badly chipped this sword is.</i>

00:13:03.700 --> 00:13:05.436
[bubbles flow]

00:13:07.708 --> 00:13:09.411
<i>It's futile.</i>

00:13:09.444 --> 00:13:10.446
<i>It's over.</i>

00:13:10.479 --> 00:13:11.916
[bubbles flow]

00:13:14.288 --> 00:13:17.360
<i>I can only hope
that help is on the way.</i>

00:13:20.266 --> 00:13:21.536
<i>Sorry, Master...</i>

00:13:22.572 --> 00:13:24.308
<i>but I'm going to die,</i>

00:13:24.341 --> 00:13:26.847
<i>so as soon as you can,</i>

00:13:26.880 --> 00:13:29.317
<i>please send
at least two Hashira.</i>

00:13:32.858 --> 00:13:34.763
[Tanjiro] What makes
you think you'll die?

00:13:34.796 --> 00:13:36.164
- Huh?

00:13:37.167 --> 00:13:38.435
Ohh.

00:13:40.975 --> 00:13:43.345
- What makes you think
you'll die?

00:13:44.715 --> 00:13:48.188
After all, nobody knows
what the future holds, right?

00:13:50.761 --> 00:13:52.430
<i>- Hold on.</i>

00:13:52.464 --> 00:13:53.900
<i>This isn't right.</i>

00:13:55.169 --> 00:13:58.308
<i>Tanjiro never said
anything like that to me.</i>

00:14:01.716 --> 00:14:05.222
<i>If not him, then who?</i>

00:14:07.127 --> 00:14:10.333
- Stay back!
I can't let you get inside!

00:14:10.366 --> 00:14:11.736
- Hyo, hyo!

00:14:11.769 --> 00:14:12.739
Why do you bother?

00:14:12.772 --> 00:14:15.377
You're only wasting my time.

00:14:15.410 --> 00:14:17.314
Or could it be
that you're foolish enough

00:14:17.347 --> 00:14:19.853
to think you're capable
of fending me off?

00:14:19.886 --> 00:14:20.854
- [whimpers]

00:14:20.887 --> 00:14:23.927
- Hyo, hyo, hyo!

00:14:23.961 --> 00:14:26.298
Well, I find that to be...

00:14:26.331 --> 00:14:27.769
just comical!

00:14:27.802 --> 00:14:29.304
- [whimpers]

00:14:29.337 --> 00:14:30.541
- [yells]
- Hyo!

00:14:30.574 --> 00:14:32.511
- [gags]

00:14:34.181 --> 00:14:35.082
[groans]

00:14:35.116 --> 00:14:37.487
- Why is it you're
so desperately defending

00:14:37.521 --> 00:14:39.925
such a pitiful-looking shack?

00:14:39.959 --> 00:14:42.565
You wouldn't be hiding
your precious village chief

00:14:42.598 --> 00:14:44.502
in this shed, now, would you?

00:14:44.535 --> 00:14:46.339
- [gasping]

00:14:46.372 --> 00:14:47.340
- Hmm?

00:14:47.373 --> 00:14:49.477
[metal scraping]

00:14:52.484 --> 00:14:54.454
Hmm?!

00:15:00.701 --> 00:15:02.872
- Extraordinary steel.

00:15:02.905 --> 00:15:05.242
What an extraordinary sword!

00:15:07.180 --> 00:15:08.917
<i>- That human is young,</i>

00:15:08.950 --> 00:15:11.856
<i>the body of someone
not yet even 40.</i>

00:15:11.890 --> 00:15:14.662
<i>There's no way
he could be chief.</i>

00:15:14.696 --> 00:15:17.868
- Such brilliant craftsmanship.

00:15:17.901 --> 00:15:20.273
This blade is stunning!

00:15:20.306 --> 00:15:22.077
- Hmm!

00:15:22.110 --> 00:15:25.884
Hey, human,
what are you doing over there?

00:15:25.918 --> 00:15:28.957
- Who created this masterpiece?

00:15:28.991 --> 00:15:31.863
By what kind of person
was this sword forged?

00:15:31.896 --> 00:15:34.067
And why did he carve
this single character,

00:15:34.100 --> 00:15:36.071
rather than his own name?

00:15:36.105 --> 00:15:38.510
No, I understand.

00:15:38.544 --> 00:15:40.279
I understand why!

00:15:41.716 --> 00:15:43.285
<i>- Damn him!</i>

00:15:43.319 --> 00:15:46.793
<i>I've never seen
such razor-sharp focus.</i>

00:15:46.827 --> 00:15:48.262
<i>He's so immersed
in what he's doing</i>

00:15:48.295 --> 00:15:50.433
<i>that he's still unaware of me!</i>

00:15:50.467 --> 00:15:54.440
<i>[growls]
I don't like this one bit.</i>

00:15:55.410 --> 00:15:57.949
<i>Even I've never
concentrated this hard</i>

00:15:57.982 --> 00:15:59.484
<i>on one of my pieces.</i>

00:15:59.519 --> 00:16:03.861
<i>As an artist, I can't help
but feel inferior to him!</i>

00:16:03.894 --> 00:16:05.764
[growls]

00:16:07.835 --> 00:16:09.270
Hyo, hyo!

00:16:09.304 --> 00:16:10.941
- Stop it!

00:16:10.975 --> 00:16:12.578
M-Mr. Haganezuka.

00:16:12.612 --> 00:16:13.980
[drop splashes]

00:16:14.013 --> 00:16:14.982
[clatter]

00:16:15.016 --> 00:16:16.686
- [breathes heavily]

00:16:16.720 --> 00:16:19.191
- Mr. Haganezuka.

00:16:19.224 --> 00:16:20.059
- What?!

00:16:20.092 --> 00:16:22.064
- [yells]
- [Kanamori yelps]

00:16:22.097 --> 00:16:25.538
- [breathing heavily]

00:16:25.571 --> 00:16:29.845
<i>[singers vocalizing]</i>

00:16:29.879 --> 00:16:32.016
<i>- [gasps]
No matter what I do,</i>

00:16:32.049 --> 00:16:34.254
<i>this man still refuses to stop!</i>

00:16:34.287 --> 00:16:37.360
- I know why he didn't do it,

00:16:37.394 --> 00:16:40.667
why he didn't carve his name
into this perfect sword!

00:16:40.700 --> 00:16:43.540
This single character
tells me this sword

00:16:43.573 --> 00:16:46.579
was forged with nothing
but pure determination.

00:16:46.613 --> 00:16:47.848
I understand it now.

00:16:47.881 --> 00:16:52.524
This sword was forged for this
sole purpose and nothing else!

00:16:53.794 --> 00:16:55.396
- Mr. Haganezuka!

00:16:57.602 --> 00:16:58.837
- [growls]

00:16:58.871 --> 00:17:00.607
<i>I can't stand this guy.</i>

00:17:00.640 --> 00:17:03.814
<i>It would be child's play
to horrifically slaughter him,</i>

00:17:03.847 --> 00:17:05.216
<i>but I want right now</i>

00:17:05.250 --> 00:17:07.588
<i>is to make this man
abandon that sword!</i>

00:17:07.621 --> 00:17:11.394
<i>I want to shatter
his concentration!</i>

00:17:16.806 --> 00:17:19.746
<i>[soft music]</i>

00:17:19.779 --> 00:17:27.327
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:17:27.360 --> 00:17:30.634
<i>- My vision
is starting to get distorted.</i>

00:17:32.638 --> 00:17:34.074
<i>I'm dying.</i>

00:17:34.107 --> 00:17:35.644
<i>I'm all out of air.</i>

00:17:37.849 --> 00:17:41.388
- Sorry, but it's not for you
to decide when it's all over.

00:17:43.894 --> 00:17:45.363
<i>- I don't understand.</i>

00:17:45.396 --> 00:17:47.333
You never told me that.

00:17:47.366 --> 00:17:49.872
- It's all gonna be okay.

00:17:49.906 --> 00:17:51.408
Just don't give up.

00:17:51.441 --> 00:17:53.780
I promise
someone's gonna save you.

00:17:55.717 --> 00:17:58.756
<i>- Really?
Leave it to someone else?</i>

00:17:59.859 --> 00:18:01.829
<i>That's the worst thing
I could do.</i>

00:18:02.965 --> 00:18:05.169
- There's a limit
to what we can do.

00:18:05.202 --> 00:18:07.239
At least, when we're alone.

00:18:07.273 --> 00:18:08.543
We all need help.

00:18:08.576 --> 00:18:10.680
There's no shame
in asking for it.

00:18:13.653 --> 00:18:17.027
<i>- But there's no one
who can save me.</i>

00:18:17.060 --> 00:18:19.430
<i>Because everyone's
weaker than I am.</i>

00:18:21.268 --> 00:18:24.107
<i>I'm the one who should
have been stronger.</i>

00:18:25.343 --> 00:18:27.313
<i>I misjudged my strength...</i>

00:18:28.348 --> 00:18:32.189
<i>and subconsciously
overestimated my own skills...</i>

00:18:33.058 --> 00:18:35.229
<i>all because I'm a Hashira.</i>

00:18:37.000 --> 00:18:39.806
- You're not wrong
about that, Muichiro.

00:18:39.839 --> 00:18:41.441
You're gonna be fine.

00:18:45.016 --> 00:18:46.217
<i>- I'm going to die,</i>

00:18:46.251 --> 00:18:48.923
<i>because that's not
the only mistake I made.</i>

00:18:49.926 --> 00:18:51.529
- [grunts]

00:18:52.932 --> 00:18:54.167
[muffled] Mr. Tokito!

00:18:54.200 --> 00:18:56.137
[normal] I won't let you die!

00:18:56.171 --> 00:18:57.607
Hang in there, Mr. Tokito!

00:18:57.641 --> 00:18:58.610
No matter what,

00:18:58.643 --> 00:19:01.215
I'm gonna get you out of there
and save you!

00:19:01.248 --> 00:19:03.285
C--Crap! What is this?

00:19:03.318 --> 00:19:06.225
It's all rubbery and disgusting!

00:19:06.258 --> 00:19:09.164
<i>- If even
I can't slash through it,</i>

00:19:09.197 --> 00:19:11.034
<i>how on earth can you?</i>

00:19:11.068 --> 00:19:15.109
<i>Not to mention, you have bigger
priorities than me right now.</i>

00:19:15.142 --> 00:19:18.248
<i>You have to protect the chief.</i>

00:19:20.252 --> 00:19:23.325
<i>Oh, I suppose
that would be beyond you.</i>

00:19:23.358 --> 00:19:26.666
<i>You should grab as many swords
as you can and run.</i>

00:19:26.699 --> 00:19:27.968
[knife pounding]

00:19:28.002 --> 00:19:29.137
<i>[gasps]</i>

00:19:29.170 --> 00:19:31.743
<i>[tense music]</i>

00:19:31.776 --> 00:19:34.080
[demon grunting]

00:19:34.113 --> 00:19:35.149
[metal clangs]

00:19:35.182 --> 00:19:37.453
<i>- What are you doing?
Behind you!</i>

00:19:37.487 --> 00:19:40.259
<i>Behind you. Behind you!</i>

00:19:42.698 --> 00:19:43.466
- [groans]

00:19:43.499 --> 00:19:45.804
- [gasping]
- [grunting]

00:19:45.838 --> 00:19:47.173
- Ugh! I'm bleeding!

00:19:47.207 --> 00:19:49.477
<i>- What are you doing?
What are you doing?</i>

00:19:49.511 --> 00:19:51.949
<i>Make a run for it!
Before it's too late!</i>

00:19:51.983 --> 00:19:53.953
- [grunts]

00:19:53.987 --> 00:19:55.557
- [groans]

00:19:55.590 --> 00:19:57.060
<i>- [gasps]</i>

00:19:57.093 --> 00:19:59.364
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:19:59.398 --> 00:20:01.602
- [grunts]
- [groaning]

00:20:04.007 --> 00:20:05.309
<i>- His solar plexus.</i>

00:20:05.342 --> 00:20:07.146
<i>He got stabbed
in his vital point.</i>

00:20:07.180 --> 00:20:09.818
- [gasping]
<i>- He's going to die.</i>

00:20:11.756 --> 00:20:13.259
<i>Why don't you get it?!</i>

00:20:13.292 --> 00:20:14.761
<i>You're not strong enough!</i>

00:20:14.795 --> 00:20:18.368
<i>Put pressure on that wound,
and get out of here, already!</i>

00:20:18.402 --> 00:20:20.974
<i>Stop trying to save me!</i>

00:20:21.007 --> 00:20:22.376
<i>You need to save yourself!</i>

00:20:22.410 --> 00:20:24.916
<i>There's nothing
you can do for me!</i>

00:20:24.949 --> 00:20:31.027
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:20:31.061 --> 00:20:32.798
[bubbles flowing]

00:20:32.832 --> 00:20:34.433
<i>[gasps]</i>

00:20:41.215 --> 00:20:43.553
- Life always rewards
good deeds.

00:20:43.586 --> 00:20:47.594
When you help others,
you're often helping yourself.

00:20:49.030 --> 00:20:52.036
- [inhaling]

00:20:53.238 --> 00:20:55.376
- Humans are incredible.

00:20:55.409 --> 00:20:58.048
They can summon
an unbelievable strength,

00:20:58.081 --> 00:20:59.417
but only when
it's for the sake

00:20:59.450 --> 00:21:01.722
of someone
other than themselves.

00:21:04.026 --> 00:21:05.763
Muichiro.

00:21:07.801 --> 00:21:09.905
<i>- Yes, I know.</i>

00:21:09.938 --> 00:21:12.110
<i>[soft music]</i>

00:21:12.143 --> 00:21:16.986
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:21:17.019 --> 00:21:19.090
<i>Mist Breathing, Second Form...</i>

00:21:19.123 --> 00:21:20.360
<i>[rising music]</i>

00:21:20.393 --> 00:21:21.962
<i>Eight-Layered Mist!</i>

00:21:23.231 --> 00:21:25.938
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

00:21:25.971 --> 00:21:27.307
[grunts]

00:21:27.340 --> 00:21:31.281
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:21:31.315 --> 00:21:33.519
<i>I remember now, Tanjiro.</i>

00:21:35.022 --> 00:21:39.532
<i>The reason I saw you,
but heard my father's words</i>

00:21:39.565 --> 00:21:42.872
<i>is because you share
the same red eyes.</i>

00:21:42.905 --> 00:21:44.876
<i>["Koi Kogare" playing]</i>

00:21:44.909 --> 00:21:51.922
<i>♪♪ ♪♪</i>

00:23:12.917 --> 00:23:15.089
[page rustles]

00:23:15.122 --> 00:23:16.892
- [grunting]

00:23:16.925 --> 00:23:20.533
<i>[mellow music]</i>

00:23:22.538 --> 00:23:24.675
- So this is what you've
been up to in secret?

00:23:24.709 --> 00:23:26.445
But why should you
have to go this far

00:23:26.478 --> 00:23:27.882
just to forge a sword?

00:23:27.915 --> 00:23:30.419
- The swordsman
puts his life on the line

00:23:30.452 --> 00:23:31.689
when he goes into battle,

00:23:31.722 --> 00:23:33.960
so it's only fair
that his swordsmith

00:23:33.993 --> 00:23:36.699
puts his life on the line
while forging his blade

00:23:36.732 --> 00:23:39.404
and pour his soul
into his sword!

00:23:39.437 --> 00:23:40.707
- Oh, yeah?

00:23:40.740 --> 00:23:44.180
Now it's time
for a Taisho-era secret!

00:23:44.214 --> 00:23:45.349
The knives he was wielding

00:23:45.382 --> 00:23:47.353
when he chased
after Mr. Tanjiro

00:23:47.386 --> 00:23:49.658
were forged by Mr. Haganezuka.

00:23:49.691 --> 00:23:51.629
But since
they're unbelievably sharp,

00:23:51.662 --> 00:23:54.568
he says he's too scared
to use them for cooking!

00:23:54.601 --> 00:23:56.639
Is that totally pointless
or what?

00:23:56.673 --> 00:23:57.440
Hmm?

00:23:57.473 --> 00:23:59.210
- [roars]

00:23:59.244 --> 00:24:00.614
- Mr. Haganezuka?

00:24:00.647 --> 00:24:02.249
- [shrieking]
- Scary, scary, scary!

00:24:02.283 --> 00:24:03.620
Mr. Haganezuka,
you're scaring me!

00:24:03.653 --> 00:24:06.692
- Next, Episode 8,
"The Mu in Muichiro."

